name: Kennedy Space Center
description: NASA's primary launch center of human spaceflight. Located on the east coast of Florida, KSC is adjacent to Cape Canaveral Space Force Station (CCSFS).

name: Baikonur Cosmodrome
description: The world's first and largest operational space launch facility located in southern Kazakhstan.

name: Guiana Space Centre
description: A French and European spaceport to the northwest of Kourou in French Guiana.
